<body>
    <h1>Safe DELETING of pods</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p>NB: This is only a valid process for a <span style=3D"color: rgb=
(76,154,255);">DEPLOYMENT</span>. </p>
<p>In this example I had a failed <span style=3D"color: rgb(255,196,0);">Ar=
goCD</span> <span style=3D"color: rgb(76,154,255);">DEPLOYMENT</span> and i=
t resulted in an issue where I needed to delete some affected pods.</p>
<p><strong><u>Genreal Scenario</u>:: </strong>So you have <span style=3D"co=
lor: rgb(54,179,126);">PODS</span> in trouble that need to be <span style=
=3D"color: rgb(76,154,255);">Deleted</span>. This even after attempting to =
delete the <span style=3D"color: rgb(54,179,126);">PODS</span> / by reversi=
ng a deployment as I did here..</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">wayne@d=
ev-dr-bastion:~$ kubectl delete -n argocd -f argocd.yaml</pre>=20
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> <span style=3D"color: rgb(54,179,126);">NODES</sp=
an> are <span style=3D"color: rgb(76,154,255);">Drained</span> by command b=
ut may have other <span style=3D"color: rgb(54,179,126);">PODS</span> activ=
e on them that are not in trouble. </p>
<p>So:: <span style=3D"color: rgb(76,154,255);">Draining</span> a <span sty=
le=3D"color: rgb(54,179,126);">NODE</span> or <span style=3D"color: rgb(76,=
154,255);">deleting</span> pods on a <span style=3D"color: rgb(54,179,126);=
">NODE</span> may disrupt deployments so proceed <span style=3D"color: rgb(=
191,38,0);">CAREFULLY</span>!</p>
<h3 id=3D"SafeDELETINGofpods-ToViewthedeployment..">To View the deployment.=
.</h3>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">wayne@d=
ev-dr-bastion:~$ kubectl get deployments -A</pre>=20
</div>
</div>
<p><code>--&gt;</code></p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;"><code>NAMESPACE &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;N=
AME &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp=
;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;READY &nbsp;&nbsp;UP=
-TO-DATE &nbsp;&nbsp;AVAILABLE &nbsp;&nbsp;AGE </code><br><code>argocd &nbs=
p;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;argocd-dex-server &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&=
nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;0/1 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbs=
p;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;0 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp=
;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;37m </code><br><code>argocd &nbsp;&nbs=
p;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;argocd-redis &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;0/1 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp=
;1 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;0 &nbs=
p;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;37m </code><br><cod=
e>argocd &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;argocd-repo-server &nbsp=
;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;0/1 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1 &nbsp;&n=
bsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;0 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nb=
sp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;37m </code><br><code>argocd &n=
bsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;argocd-server &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nb=
sp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;0/1 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&n=
bsp;1 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;0 &=
nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;37m </code><br><=
code>kube-system &nbsp;&nbsp;calico-kube-controllers &nbsp;&nbsp;1/1 &nbsp;=
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&=
nbsp;&nbsp;1 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;10=
d </code><br><code>kube-system &nbsp;&nbsp;coredns &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nb=
sp;&nbsp;2/2 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&=
nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;10d </code><br><code>kube-system &nbsp;&nbsp;dns-autoscale=
r &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1/1 &nb=
sp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbs=
p;&nbsp;&nbsp;1 &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp=
;10d</code><br><br></p>
<h2 id=3D"SafeDELETINGofpods-Step0:FindoutWhat=E2=80=99sWhatwiththedeployme=
nt">Step 0: Find out What=E2=80=99s What with the deployment</h2>
<p>Find the Broken <span style=3D"color: rgb(54,179,126);">PODS</span> with=
 their <span style=3D"color: rgb(54,179,126);">NODES</span>.</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">wayne@d=
ev-dr-bastion:~$ kubectl get pods -A -o wide | grep argocd</pre>=20
</div>
</div>
<p><code>--&gt;</code></p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;"><code>argocd argocd-application-controlle=
r-0 0/1 ImagePullBackOff 0 8m10s 10.233.96.4 dev-worker-2 &lt;none&gt; &lt;=
none&gt;</code></p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;"><code>argocd argocd-dex-server-68c7bf5fdd=
-5pj4q 0/1 Init:ImagePullBackOff 0 8m10s 10.233.96.3 dev-worker-2 &lt;none&=
gt; &lt;none&gt;</code></p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;"><code>argocd argocd-redis-7547547c4f-ljrf=
c 0/1 ImagePullBackOff 0 8m10s 10.233.102.4 dev-worker-0 &lt;none&gt; &lt;n=
one&gt;</code></p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;"><code>argocd argocd-repo-server-58f87478b=
8-2qmx4 0/1 ImagePullBackOff 0 8m10s 10.233.97.3 dev-worker-1 &lt;none&gt; =
&lt;none&gt;</code></p>
<p style=3D"margin-left: 30.0px;"><code>argocd argocd-server-6f4fcdc5dc-4dc=
t7 0/1 ImagePullBackOff 0 8m10s 10.233.102.5 dev-worker-0 &lt;none&gt; &lt;=
none&gt;</code></p>
<p></p>
<p><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,86,48);">.. So</span> <code>dev-worker-1</=
code><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,86,48);"> .. </span><code>dev-worker-0</=
code><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,86,48);"> ..</span> <code>dev-worker-2</=
code><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,86,48);"> </span><span style=3D"color: r=
gb(54,179,126);">NODES</span><span style=3D"color: rgb(255,86,48);"> are af=
fected</span></p>
<h2 id=3D"SafeDELETINGofpods-Step:1MarkthesenodesasUnSchedulable">Step:1 Ma=
rk these nodes as UnSchedulable</h2>
<p>&nbsp;I.e Cordon Off the nodes affected so that no new pods will get sch=
eduled to the node while you are prepping it for removal or maintenance. Yo=
u use the the&nbsp;<code>kubectl</code>&nbsp;<code>cordon</code>&nbsp;comma=
nd</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">wayne@d=
ev-dr-bastion:~$ kubectl cordon dev-worker-0
wayne@dev-dr-bastion:~$ kubectl cordon dev-worker-1
wayne@dev-dr-bastion:~$ kubectl cordon dev-worker-2</pre>=20
</div>
</div>
<h2 id=3D"SafeDELETINGofpods-Step:2Nowyoucanworkonmovingpodsoffofthenode.">=
&nbsp;Step:2 Now you can work on moving pods off of the node. </h2>
<p>If you need more <span style=3D"color: rgb(76,154,255);">replicas</span>=
 for the <span style=3D"color: rgb(76,154,255);">DEPLOYMENT</span> when you=
 have failed <span style=3D"color: rgb(76,154,255);">PODS</span> but still =
have a working <span style=3D"color: rgb(76,154,255);">DEPLOYMENT</span> yo=
u can use increase the <span style=3D"color: rgb(76,154,255);">replicas</sp=
an> by one so that the other nodes pick up the workload, delete the effecte=
d <span style=3D"color: rgb(76,154,255);">POD</span> (by Name) and then res=
et the <span style=3D"color: rgb(76,154,255);">replicas</span> to the origi=
nal value.</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">kubectl=
 scale deployment argocd --replicas=3D2
kubectl delete pod argocd-redis-7547547c4f-ljrfc  =20
  ... &lt;&lt;other pods delete&gt;&gt;
kubectl scale deployment argocd --replicas=3D1</pre>=20
</div>
</div>
<h2 id=3D"SafeDELETINGofpods-Step:3NB!!!!AllowpodsbackontothenodesinCORDONm=
ode.">Step:3 NB!!!! Allow pods back onto the nodes in CORDON mode.</h2>
<p>Use the&nbsp;<code>kubectl&nbsp;uncordon</code>&nbsp;command to allow sc=
heduling on the node again. </p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"syntaxhighlighter-pre" data-syntaxhighlighter-params=3D"brush=
: java; gutter: false; theme: Confluence" data-theme=3D"Confluence">wayne@d=
ev-dr-bastion:~$ kubectl uncordon dev-worker-0
wayne@dev-dr-bastion:~$ kubectl uncordon dev-worker-1
wayne@dev-dr-bastion:~$ kubectl uncordon dev-worker-2</pre>=20
</div>
</div>
